  <!-- Hero2 Widget ******************* -->

  <Hero
    id="hero"
    title="Camila Alvarez"
    tagline="Personal Portfolio and Blog"
    actions={[{ variant: "primary", target: '_blank', text: 'Check Out My Blog', href: '/blog' }]}
  >
    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      I'm a university student majoring in math and data science and analytics. Here, you'll find my work, projects, and thoughts on topics ranging from machine learning to mathematical theory. My aim is to make these complex subjects accessible and interesting, whether you're a fellow student or simply curious about the intersection of data and math. Thanks for visiting, and I hope you find something here that piques your interest.
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    id="about"
    columns={3}
    items={[
      {
        icon: 'tabler:brand-github',
        callToAction: {
          target: '_blank',
          text: 'Github',
          href: 'https://github.com/cam-alvarez',
        },
      },
      {
        icon: 'tabler:brand-linkedin',
        callToAction: {
          target: '_blank',
          text: 'LinkedIn',
          href: '#',
        },
      },
      {
        icon: 'tabler:brand-google',
        callToAction: {
          target: '_blank',
          text: 'Email',
          href: '#',
        },
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: '/memoji.png',
      alt: 'Colorful Image',
      style: 'background-color: transparent; opacity: 0.8;',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">About me</h3>
      <p>
        Hello! I'm Camila, a passionate student majoring in Mathematics and Data Science & Analytics. I fell in love with the abstract beauty and endless possibilities of math, and I'm fascinated by the power of data to solve real-world problems. I'm currently honing my skills in Python programming and statistical analysis, aiming to become proficient in machine learning techniques.
      </p>
      <br />
      <!-- Using text-lg to make the title smaller than the parent title -->
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-lg mb-1">Why Math?</h4>
      <p>
        For me, math is more than just equations and theorems; it's a creative art form. The more I delved into advanced topics, the more I realized the creative thought processes behind problem-solving. The complexity and elegance of mathematical logic never ceases to amaze me.
      </p>
      <br />
      <!-- Using text-lg to make the title smaller than the parent title -->
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-lg mb-1">Why Data Science?</h4>
      <p>
        Data Science is like the bridge between theory and application for me. I find it thrilling to leverage mathematical concepts to draw insights from data and create impactful solutions.
      </p>
    </Fragment>



